Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:06.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:22.04,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:28.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:36.63,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:42.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:51.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:58.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:02.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:06.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:12.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:29.72,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:06.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这份真情实感　好想将它传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.30,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不沉溺于一去不返的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:22.04,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧紧拥抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:28.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷于那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:36.63,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方应该有什么正等待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:42.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝着那未完结的故事　飞奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀着一颗真诚的心向着那千难万险之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:51.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}张开心灵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:58.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循环传递着一个讯息　幸福就存于这胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:02.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下来的少许勇气　尽管须以眼泪相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:06.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但这或许正是变强的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:12.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温暖的迭句　想要永远将这份珍重守护
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心绪交织　感受着这其中的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以说没有人是孤身只影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:29.72,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片蓝天下　好想将这份真情实感传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:19.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:28.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:37.80,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:46.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:49.15,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:57.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:06.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:15.83,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:27.03,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:19.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣着内心深处收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:28.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跃入未知的前方　那里有什么正等待着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:37.80,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是与未来共鸣　不断忆起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:46.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会生出勇气　就能变得坚强　也就不再是独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:49.15,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（让你倾听）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:57.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定会与你相遇　我会带着真诚的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:06.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接梦想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:15.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与其坐拥这无限的时刻　倒不如追赶那绚烂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:27.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　总有一天会让你倾听那梦中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:49.46,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第6碗  家里煮的饭、冷了也觉得热乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思啊  问你借了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一口气读完它们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这漫画的确有很多设定不集中  读完一转眼就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错啊  到一半会分不清敌我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以为40卷前死掉的角色突然出现我也吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  没错啊  什么嘛  你也不是很清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  你最喜欢哪个角色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…夏奈姐最喜欢哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我可不喜欢那么优柔寡断的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着都有点心急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我读完再促膝长谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗士  冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我很欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重的  我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么点没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…请小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真能下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好迟啊  出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么特殊的事却回来迟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟点回来理由这么重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在照顾仓鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修一和我负责饲养它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  就因为这个啊  真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些漫画是从冬木那借来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还真执着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这部长篇漫画全收齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结局是成为贵族还是王族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋想看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下冬木就是好孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:03:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我都用敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是尊敬长辈的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬语我还是会用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看对方是谁就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是本质不同啊  明智君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不管对谁都笑着说敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经积得很深了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面也好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒冷可是女人的天敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可不能掉以轻心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没在胡扯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜是久违的大雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不太现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp225}　{\fsp1}gratin{\fsp1}{\r}\N两袋冷冻法式奶汁干酪烙菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边只有切片面包和意大利面而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些食材真够微妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一手  把剩下的东西全扔进火锅做大杂烩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸黑会餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃气罐没了  储藏罐也没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要去买菜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经积得很深了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面也好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃现成的应付一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那赶紧准备起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一堆漫画要读
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭做好了叫我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当自己是千金大小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱了  满足了  开心了  塞满了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一厘米都塞不进了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  几乎把剩下的材料全用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天不去补习一定要去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便也把这个买了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一包了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺道去下干洗店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了把外套拿回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁送去的谁去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样明天再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪还在下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错  明天明天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的天气可出不了门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚刚在电梯口碰到邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是接下来还要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐槽吐错地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去干洗店拿衣服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪有没有积起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积得好深了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白的雪白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷起来了  回房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟寒冷是女人的天敌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外面去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨磨蹭蹭的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪天在院子里到处跑才是正解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后打算缩在被炉里吗  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你在那边发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来劲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈选手投出…第一球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你狠  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:11.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进到鼻子里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  站起来千秋  你不会就这点本事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡扯  我会去医院看你的  绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得这东西有些异样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面我来教你什么叫「Winter sports」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会点啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开演啊  开演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在胡扯些啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该回去了  好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  差不多就到最佳时机了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在策划什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也烧得太久了点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算哪门子的最佳时机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等叻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「久等叻」你个头啊  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂风情的小鬼给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  这可是下雪天才能享受到的热水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上…这开放感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍温了一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太温了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再烧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这样泡澡的也只有自家的浴缸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话别这么刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一会再出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  雪之夜第二幕现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得安心了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面下着雪  却窝在被炉里吃点心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  停电了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  马上就修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴喊喊就能暖和起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为冷才喊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  不会停太长时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那之前还活着的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我有点困了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没干粮  通信又断了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能死在这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋千秋…快说啊  那句台词
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦  只有一亿元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢  那是什么场景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  貌似有这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很冷了你就不能消停一会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室  应该还有点余温  去暖一会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸黑浴也不坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变凉了  而且窗户没关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁把窗户打开的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你呗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  是我  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把窗户关上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来  会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把窗户关上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有点恶心能不能别捏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能这样取暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么贪心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这个取暖方法就够好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了  想吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有倒是有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗  我要吃我想吃一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冻得硬邦邦可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了那个  都凉到骨子里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕有热水也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用  因为没煤气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小麦粉  水和鸡蛋搅在一起会有烤薄饼的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做做看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这可不是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力还没恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修复还真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时不觉得有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没电原来这么不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下这么大的雪居然停电就是松散的铁证
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责人快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫来想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好教育他一番好让类似的事别发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点子不错  好好地做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩晴天娃娃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想死是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  偶尔这样过一晚也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  冬木爸爸不在家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一个人没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去看看他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么担心他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定有很多取暖设备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是小孩睡得也太早了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对方是小学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算看上去是那样…春香  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道发生什么怪事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  可能已经睡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  好了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为邻居要互相帮助嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木遇到什么麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲了很久都没出来  还以为你死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开这种不吉利的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正担心冬木你一个人该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家为什么不马上开门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我刚想睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这一身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  刚想换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  把小炉子用的燃气罐借我们一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  请用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:15:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连替换的都有啊  真有心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很冷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了冬木  到我们家玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下小炉子也能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊  不用客气的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秉烛夜谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  不知道爸爸什么时候回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大雪天回到家见我不在  肯定会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很想来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个能干的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一个人应该没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  突然怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么不想来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那样  怕爸爸担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是边说边在想怎么拒绝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来就来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不老老实实说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样  我并不是很想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你这德性我就生气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样…就别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？想说什么就大声说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…夏奈姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们也加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦  两位准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不会手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要和他分在一组
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心别人了  赶快还击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样完全不能还击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样组队完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我来扔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你负责捏雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手冻僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有火就觉得暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真感谢文明的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也多亏了冬木啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得  就住下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真缓和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要不是停电也不会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就这样取暖就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  好像来电了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬木  在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木在铲雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错  真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这么个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫肉球摸起来真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似根据猫生活的环境  软度也会有所不同哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野猫常常在坚硬的路面上走  肉球也就硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.51,0:23:45.06,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(370,0)}第7碗  「越嚼越甜哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家猫就软软的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.59,0:23:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  下次试着摸摸肉球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
